def get_century(year: str) -> str:
    n = (int(year) - 1) // 100 - 1
    suffix = 'th' if n < 20 else {1: 'st', 2: 'nd', 3: 'rd'}.get(n % 10, 'th')
    return f'{n}{suffix}'
